---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Sifath Arora — a Redmond High School freshman passionate about dentistry, science, music, and community advocacy."
>
  <div class="container page-header page-header--wide">
    <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
    <h1>Hi, I'm Sifath</h1>
    <p>
      Freshman at Redmond High School exploring dentistry, science, and community advocacy.
      <a href="mailto:sifathkaurarora@gmail.com">sifathkaurarora@gmail.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container prose">
    <p>
      Hi! My name is Sifath Arora, and I'm a freshman at Redmond High School. I've always
      been interested in science, especially topics related to health, which is what first
      got me thinking about dentistry. I like that dentistry is hands-on and allows you to
      help people feel more confident through their smiles. It's a career that combines
      problem-solving, creativity, and working closely with others, which really appeals to me.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of school, I enjoy staying involved in different activities and pushing myself
      to learn new skills. I play violin as First Chair in orchestra, compete on varsity
      slow-pitch softball, and have spent eight years in Destination Imagination — advancing
      to Global Finals five times and earning 10th place worldwide in the improvisational challenge.
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm also deeply committed to advocacy and education. I've participated in Sikh Advocacy
      Day with state legislators, volunteer weekly at a religious school teaching Punjabi,
      Sikh history, and core academics, and write about Sikh identity, student experiences,
      and cultural representation on my blog.
    </p>

    <p>
      This website is a place where I document my interests, growth, and experiences as I
      explore dentistry and move through high school.
    </p>

    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <ul class="interest-tags">
      <li>Dentistry</li>
      <li>Biology</li>
      <li>Healthcare</li>
      <li>Community Service</li>
      <li>Education</li>
      <li>Cultural Advocacy</li>
      <li>Music</li>
      <li>Public Speaking</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="container resume-block" id="resume">
    <p class="section-label">Resume</p>
    <h2>Sifath Arora</h2>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h3>Education</h3>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Redmond High School</strong>
        <span>Redmond, WA &mdash; 9th Grade | GPA: 4.0</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h3>Skills</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Strong written and verbal communication</li>
        <li>Leadership and mentorship abilities</li>
        <li>Public speaking and advocacy experience</li>
        <li>Experience working with elementary and middle school students</li>
        <li>Research and presentation skills</li>
        <li>Organized, responsible, and dependable</li>
        <li>Team collaboration and time management</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h3>Extracurricular Activities</h3>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Varsity Slow-Pitch Softball</strong>
        <span>Redmond High School</span>
        <p>Selected to compete at the varsity level, demonstrating teamwork, discipline, and commitment to team success.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Orchestra (Violin, First Chair)</strong>
        <p>Perform as First Chair Violinist, demonstrating musical excellence, leadership, and dedication.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Destination Imagination</strong>
        <p>Competed for 8 years and advanced to Global Finals 5 times. Earned 10th Place Worldwide in the Improvisational Challenge at Global Finals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Badminton</strong>
        <p>Participate in recreational and school-level play, building agility, discipline, and sportsmanship.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>DECA</strong>
        <p>Prepared roleplay and case-study presentations in Business Law and Ethics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Dental Supply Drives (Planned)</strong>
        <p>Organizing community initiatives to promote oral health access and awareness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Science Olympiad</strong>
        <p>Key middle school team member, earning Top 3 placements in multiple regional and state competitions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>National Junior Honor Society</strong>
        <p>Active member contributing to service projects and leadership initiatives.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h3>Leadership &amp; Advocacy</h3>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Sikh Advocacy Day Participant</strong>
        <p>Engaged in civic discussions with state legislators. Advocated for inclusive education and Sikh representation in curriculum.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Education &amp; Culture Blog Creator</strong>
        <p>Research and publish content focused on Sikh identity, student experiences, and cultural representation.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h3>Volunteer Experience</h3>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <strong>Religious School Volunteer</strong>
        <span>Federal Way, WA (Weekly)</span>
        <p>Teach Punjabi language, Sikh history, cultural hymns, and core academic subjects to underprivileged students. Organized and led math competitions and mentor students in cultural awareness and leadership.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h3>Achievements</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>10th Place Worldwide, Destination Imagination Global Finals (Improvisational Challenge)</li>
        <li>Regional Winner, Sikh Youth Symposium</li>
        <li>3rd Place, Life Science &amp; Dentistry Research Capstone Project</li>
        <li>Winner, Research Capstone Final Contact Contest</li>
        <li>First Chair Violinist, School Orchestra</li>
        <li>5-Time Destination Imagination Global Finalist</li>
        <li>Sikh Advocacy Day Participant</li>
        <li>Top 3 placements in Science Olympiad regional and state competitions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>
      I'd love to connect! Reach me at
      <a href="mailto:sifathkaurarora@gmail.com">sifathkaurarora@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .interest-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .interest-tags li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  .resume-block {
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }

  .resume-block h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
